            <title>[HTTPCLIENT-594] HttpMethodBase#aborted variable mistakenly declared transient instead of volatile</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HTTPCLIENT-594</link>
                <project id="12310360" key="HTTPCLIENT">HttpComponents HttpClient</project>
                        <description>HttpMethodBase#aborted variable mistakenly declared transient instead of volatile. This is quite nasty. &lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
